pullrequest.title: Building Editor: Delete child windows and doors before deleting wall

content.raw: One small thing: whenever I delete a door with a wall on it, I get a gzerr: "Manip  not found" (BuildingMaker line 275). Wonder if we can clean this up, since it's an error that gets printed on otherwise normal behavior.
